name: Rare Beauty by Selena Gomez
bio:
Made to feel good in, without hiding what makes you unique. 1% of all sales go to support mental health. 
@Sephora @SpaceNK

captions:
Join Global Stylist @cynth_pop using all of Mabel Mora from @onlymurdershulu’s favorites from Rare Beauty 🙌 

Save 20% when you buy 3 or more products from Mabel Mora’s look, available only at RareBeauty.com. Offer ends 8/22 and available while supplies last only at www.rarebeauty.com. Limited to US only for 13+; one discount per customer. Terms apply. 

Mabel’s faves: 
Perfect Strokes Matte Liquid Liner
Perfect Strokes Universal Volumizing Mascara
Soft Pinch Liquid Blush in Hope
Kind Words Matte Lip Liner in Humble
Stay Vulnerable Glossy Lip Balm in Nearly Neutral
Always an Optimist 4-in-1 Mist

Stream NEW episodes of @onlymurdershulu every Tuesday🕵

#OnlyMurdersxRareBeauty #rarebeauty #onlymurdersonhulu #mabelmora

As a proud partner in #MentalHealthAction Day, we're challenging you to take action on supporting your own mental health. Join Rare Beauty Global Stylist @cynth_pop & Sephora Beauty Director @ladyymelinda as they get chat on all the actions they take to care for their mental well-being, including getting ready with makeup made to feel good in.

—

If you are in the United States and need suicide or mental health-related crisis support, or are worried about someone else, please call or text 988. Your call will be directed to a local mental health crisis center.

If you are located internationally, please visit findahelpline.com for a global list of helplines, hotlines, and crisis lines that can support you.

Hang out with the Rare Beauty team as they chat all about the latest addition to the Soft Pinch family! From Founder @selenagomez’s vision for the Soft Pinch Tinted Lip Oil, the 2-year development process, to the newest shades of Soft Pinch Liquid Blush, Warm Wishes Effortless Bronzer Stick, and the Discovery Eyeshadow Palette in Give Yourself Grace.

Social & Content Manager @richhomielog (she/her)

Director of Product Development @dirtymelodies (she/her)

Global Stylist @cynth_pop (she/her)

Pro Artist @kourtney_nicole_ (she/her)

 Shop it all now only @sephora, Sephora @kohls, @spacenk, and rarebeauty.com

Global Stylist @cynth_pop (she/her) shares everything you need to know on the newest shades of Warm Wishes Effortless Bronzer Stick, Soft Pinch Liquid Blush (launching March 30), and Discovery Eyeshadow Palette in Give Yourself Grace.

Thank you to everyone who joined. 💗 Congrats to our giveaway winners @azizaabed12, @jackie_lopez26, and @xyadiraa!

Global Stylist @cynth_pop (she/her) and Pro Artist @_kourtney_nicole (she/her) are answering all the questions you have on ✨NEW Positive Light Under Eye Brightener.✨ Keep watching to get the deets on getting that instant no-makeup-makeup look.
 
Positive Light Under Eye Brightener launches only @sephora and Sephora @kohls on December 23 and @spacenk on December 26

Join the Rare Beauty team to chat about our latest launch – NEW Positive Light Silky Touch Highlighter, their go-to shade, how they like to apply, and what it really means to shine your brightest. ✨
 
Global Retail Marketing Manager @paulettexcasi wears Exhilarate – champagne gold
Pro Artist @kourtney_nicole_wears Flaunt – true gold
Global Stylist @cynth_pop wears Mesmerize – rose bronze 
 
Now available online at @sephora, Sephora at @kohls, @spacenk, and rarebeauty.com!

Hey friends! It’s Pro Artist @_kourtney_nicole here, sharing my go-to #rareroutine while answering your questions. Have more? Leave them in the comments below and I’ll try my best to get back to you all. ❤️

Join Pro Artist @_kourtney_nicole as she shares more on our feel-good gifting sets for the holiday 
season – Soft Pinch Liquid Blush 3 Piece Set, Kind Words Mini Matte Lip Duo and the Perfect Strokes 
Eye Essentials Set! Now available only @sephora, @spacenk and rarebeauty.com!

Celebrate our 2nd birthday with Global Stylist, @cynth_pop (she/her) as she recreates Founder @selenagomez’s most iconic look from the last year (that you all voted on 😉).
 
The deets ⬇️
Liquid Touch Foundation in 180W
Liquid Touch Brightening Concealer in 180W
Brow Harmony Shape & Fill Duo in Brown
Warm Wishes Effortless Bronzer Stick in Always Sunny on eyes and cheeks
Discovery Eyeshadow Palette - True To Myself in Loyal, Undeniable, Genuine & Positive
Perfect Strokes Universal Volumizing Mascara
Positive Light Liquid Luminizer in Transcend
Stay Vulnerable Glossy Lip Balm in Nearly Neutral

#rarebeauty #rareroutine #selenagomez

Join Global Stylist, @cynth_pop (she/her) as she recreates Mabel Mora’s #rareroutine, created by Makeup Designer/Department Head @jac_risotto from Season 2 of @onlymurdershulu! Want to shop her look? Now you can!
 
We’re partnering with our friends @Hulu and Mabel’s sharing her Rare Beauty favorites now only at rarebeauty.com 🔎💄 Save 20% when you buy 3 or more. Use code MABEL20 at checkout, ends 8/30. 
 
p.s. Besties, new episodes of Only Murders In The Building drop every Tuesday on Hulu! 

#OnlyMurdersxRareBeauty #rarebeauty #selenagomez
